text: Christelle Morançais (born 28 January 1975) is a French politician. She is the current Regional Council President for the Pays de la Loire region in France. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:Politicians from Pays de la Loire Category:People from Le Mans Category:Presidents of French regions and overseas collectivities Category:21st-century French women politicians
title: Christelle Morançais
